### Pseudocode

<CodeBlock language="text" showNumberOfLines={15} fontStyle="normal">
```pseudocode
maxConsecutiveOnes(arr, n){
    /* cur = length of current continuous 1s segment */
    cur = 0

    /* best = maximum consecutive 1s seen so far */
    best = 0

    /* Traverse the array once */
    for i = 0 to n - 1 {

        if arr[i] == 1 {
            /* Extend the current segment of 1s */
            cur = cur + 1

            /* Update the best answer if needed */
            if cur > best {
                best = cur
            }
        }
        else {
            /* Break in 1s segment, reset current count */
            cur = 0
        }
    }

    /* Return the maximum consecutive 1s */
    return best
}
```
