### Pseudo Code


<CodeBlock language="text" showNumberOfLines={15} fontStyle="normal">

```plaintext
missingNumber(arr, n) {
    /* Iterate through all numbers from 1 to n */
    for i = 1 to n {
        /* Assume the current number i is not present. We will search the array to verify. */
        present = 0
        /* Scan the array to check if i exists */
        for j = 0 to n - 2 {

            /* If the current array element matches i, mark it as present and stop searching. */
            if i == arr[j] {
                present = 1
                break
            }
        }

        /* If after scanning the array, i was not found, then i is the missing number. */
        if present == 0 {
            return i
        }
    }

    /* If no missing number is found (edge case), return -1 to indicate failure. */
    return -1
}
```

</CodeBlock>


