### Pseudo Code


<CodeBlock language="text" showNumberOfLines={15} fontStyle="normal">

```plaintext
missingNumber(arr, n) {
    /* Initialize sum1 to store the sum of array elements */
    sum1 = 0
    /* Traverse the array and compute the sum of present numbers */
    for i = 0 to n - 2 {
        /* Add each element to sum1 */
        sum1 = sum1 + arr[i]
    }
    /* Compute the expected sum of numbers from 1 to n using the mathematical formula n * (n + 1) / 2 */
    sum2 = (n * (n + 1)) / 2
    /* The missing number is the difference between the expected sum and the actual sum */
    return sum2 - sum1
}
```

</CodeBlock>

