```pseudocode
isSorted(arr, n) {
    /* Traverse from first element to second last element */
    for i from 0 to n-2 {
        /* If any element is greater than the next one, array is not sorted in non-decreasing order */
        if( arr[i] > arr[i+1] ) {
            return False
        }
    }

    /* If no violating pair is found, array is sorted */
    return True
}

```

