### Pseudocode

<CodeBlock language="text" showNumberOfLines={15} fontStyle="normal">

```pseudocode
removeDuplicates(arr, n){
    /* Initialize a set to store only unique elements */
    Initialize set s

    /* Traverse the array and insert each element into the set (duplicates are automatically ignored) */
    for i from 0 to n-1 {
        s.add(arr[i])
    }

    /* j will track the index for rewriting unique elements into arr */
    j = 0
    /* Copy unique elements from set back into the array */
    for k in s {
        arr[j] = k
        j = j + 1
    }

    /* Return count of unique elements (same as j after copying) */
    return s.size()
}

```

</CodeBlock>

