<CodeBlock language="text" showNumberOfLines={15} fontStyle="normal">

```plainText
removeDuplicates(arr, n){
    /* i points to the index of the last unique element found so far */
    i = 0
    /* j scans the array from index 1 to n-1 */
    for j from 1 to n-1 {
        /* If current element is different from last unique element */
        if ( arr[i] != arr[j] ) {
            /* Place this new unique element at the next position */
            arr[i+1] = arr[j]
            /* Move i to the new last unique position */
            i++
        }
    }

    /* Total number of unique elements is i + 1 */
    return i + 1
}

```

