### Pseudo Code

<CodeBlock language="text" showNumberOfLines={15} fontStyle="normal">
```pseudocode
bubbleSort(array, n):
    /* Outer loop for each pass through the array*/
    for i from 0 to n - 1:

        /* Track if a swap happened to optimize for already sorted arrays*/
        swapped = false

        /* Inner loop to compare adjacent elements */
        /* The last i elements are already in place */
        for j from 0 to n - i - 2:

            if array[j] > array[j + 1]:
                /* Swap the elements */
                temp = array[j]
                array[j] = array[j + 1]
                array[j + 1] = temp

                swapped = true

        /* If no two elements were swapped by inner loop, then break*/
        if swapped == false:
            break
```
</CodeBlock>


