  </iframe>
</div>

### Pseudocode

<CodeBlock language="text" showNumberOfLines={15} fontStyle="normal">
```plaintext
upperBound(arr, n, x)
{
    /* low and high define the current binary search range */
    low = 0
    high = n - 1

    /* Default answer is n (means: no element > x found) */
    ans = n

    /* Binary search to find first index with value > x */
    while low <= high {
        /* Find the middle index */
        mid = (low + high) / 2

        if arr[mid] > x {
            /* mid can be an upper bound, store it */
            ans = mid

            /* Try to find a smaller valid index on the left */
            high = mid - 1
        } else {
            /* arr[mid] <= x, so upper bound must be on the right */
            low = mid + 1
        }
    }

    /* Return the upper bound index */
    return ans
}
```
</CodeBlock>

