  </iframe>
</div>

### Pseudo Code


<CodeBlock language="text" showNumberOfLines={15} fontStyle="normal">

```pseudocode
decimal_to_binary(n)
{
    /*Store binary digits.*/

    s = ""

    /*Divide by 2 until n becomes 0.*/
    while (n != 0)
    {
        /*Append remainder (0 or 1).*/
        if (n % 2 == 0)
            s += "0"
        else
            s += "1"

        /*Update n.*/
        n = n / 2
    }

    /*Reverse to get correct order.*/
    reverse(s)

    /*Return result.*/
    return s
}

```
</CodeBlock>

###Dry Run

