### Pseudo Code


<CodeBlock language="text" showNumberOfLines={15} fontStyle="normal">

```plaintext
solve(i, sum, n) {
    /* Base condition:
       Stop recursion when i exceeds n and return the accumulated sum */
    if i == n + 1 {
        return sum
    }

    /* Recursive call:
       Add current number to sum and move to next number */
    return solve(i + 1, sum + i, n)
}

recursionSum(n) {
    /* Start recursion from 0 with initial sum 0 */
    return solve(0, 0, n)
}

```

</CodeBlock>

