<CodeBlock language="text" showNumberOfLines={15} fontStyle="normal">

```
lcm(A, B) {
    greater = max(A, B)  /* Find the greater of A and B */
    smallest = min(A, B)  /* Find the smaller of A and B */
    i = greater  /* Start from the greater number */

    while true {
        if (i % smallest == 0) {
            /* If i is divisible by the smallest number, i is the LCM */
            return i
        }
        i = i + greater  /* Increment i by the greater number */
    }
}
```
