### Pseudocode

<CodeBlock language="text" showNumberOfLines={15} fontStyle="normal">

```Pseudocode
moveZerosToEnd(arr, n){
    /* Initialize a container to store non-zero elements */
    Initialize a container v // In C++ v is a vector, in Java and Python v is a List

    /* Traverse the array and add non-zero elements to container v */
    for i from 0 to n-1 {
        if ( arr[i] != 0 ) {
            v.add(arr[i])
        }
    }

    /* Copy elements from container v back into the array */
    j = 0
    for k in v {
        arr[j] = k
        j = j + 1
    }

    /* Fill the remaining positions of the array with zeros */
    for i from v.size() to n-1 {
        arr[i] = 0
    }
}

```

</CodeBlock>

### Code Implementation

