### Pseudocode

<CodeBlock language="text" showNumberOfLines={15} fontStyle="normal">

```Pseudocode
moveZerosToEnd(arr, n){
    /* Initialize i to track the position for non-zero elements */
    i = 0
    /* Traverse the array */
    for j from 0 to n-1 {

        /* If the current element is non-zero, swap it with the element at index i */
        if ( arr[j] != 0 ) {
            swap( arr[i], arr[j] )
            /* Increment i to move the position for the next non-zero element */
            i = i + 1
        }
    }
}

```

