```Pseudocode
isPowerOfTwo(n)
{
    /*Power of 2 numbers are positive.*/
    if (n <= 0)
        return false

    /*Keep dividing by 2 while the number is even. */
    while (n % 2 == 0)
        n = n / 2

    /*If we finally reach 1, it is a power of 2. */
    if (n == 1)
        return true
    else
        return false
}

```
