### Pseudo Code


<CodeBlock language="text" showNumberOfLines={15} fontStyle="normal">

```
manipulateArray(arr, n, k) {
    /* Initialize the middle index to 0 */
    middleIndex = 0                 
    /* Check if the array size is even */    
    if(n % 2 == 0) { 
        /* Set middleIndex to the first middle element */
        middleIndex = (n / 2) - 1   
    }
    else {
        /* Set middleIndex to the exact middle element */
        middleIndex = n / 2         
    }
    /* Multiply the middle element by k */
    arr[middleIndex] *= k           
    /* Print each element in a space-separated format */
    for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
        print(arr[i] + " ")         
    }
}
```

