```
validAnagram(s1, s2) {
    if (length(s1) != length(s2)) {
        return false /*--- If lengths are different, return false ---*/
    }

    sort(s1) /*--- Sort the characters in s1 ---*/
    sort(s2) /*--- Sort the characters in s2 ---*/

    if (s1 == s2) {
        return true /*--- If the sorted strings are identical, return true ---*/
    } else {
        return false /*--- If the sorted strings are not identical, return false ---*/
    }
}
```

</CodeBlock>

