# Right Half Pyramid

### Intuition 

* The number of stars on each line increases one by one as you go down.

* For each line, print the same number of stars as the current line number.

* Move to a new line after printing all stars for that row.

* Repeat this process until all lines are printed.


### Approach

* Start from the first row and go up to the last row.

* On each row, print as many stars as the row number.

* Move to a new line after printing stars for that row.

* Repeat until all rows are printed.




