<CodeBlock language="text" showNumberOfLines={15} fontStyle="normal">
```
minBitFlips(source, target){
    /* XOR highlights the positions where bits differ:
       bit = 1 means source and target differ at that position */
    n = source XOR target

    /* count how many differing bits (set bits) are present */
    count = 0

    while n != 0 {
        /* One flip is needed for each set bit */
        count = count + 1

        /* Remove the rightmost set bit from n */
        n = n AND (n - 1)
    }

    /* Total flips needed equals number of set bits in XOR */
    return count
}
```
</CodeBlock>

