### Pseudo Code


<CodeBlock language="text" showNumberOfLines={15} fontStyle="normal">

```
checkAutomorphicNumber(num) {
    /* Compute the square of the given number */
    square = num * num
    /* Initialize mod to 10 to start checking the last digit(s) */
    mod = 10
    /* Store num in temp so we can count its digits without changing num */
    temp = num

    /* Increase mod according to the number of digits in num */
    while temp >= 10 {
        /* Multiply mod by 10 for each extra digit in num */
        mod = mod * 10
        /* Remove the last digit from temp */
        temp = temp / 10
    }

    /* Check if the last digits of square are equal to num */
    return square % mod == num
}
```

