### Pseudocode

<CodeBlock language="text" showNumberOfLines={15} fontStyle="normal">

```
secondLargestDigit(num) {
    /* Initialize largest and secondlargest as -1 */
    largest = -1
    secondlargest = -1

    /* Copy num into temp so we can process its digits */
    temp = num

    /* Traverse all digits of the number */
    while temp {
        /* Extract the last digit */
        rem = temp % 10

        /* If current digit is greater than largest,
           update both largest and secondlargest */
        if rem > largest {
            secondlargest = largest
            largest = rem
        }
        /* If current digit lies between largest and secondlargest,
           update secondlargest */
        else if rem > secondlargest AND rem < largest {
            secondlargest = rem
        }

        /* Remove the last digit from temp */
        temp = temp / 10
    }

    /* Return the second largest distinct digit */
    return secondlargest
}
```

