### Pseudo Code


<CodeBlock language="text" showNumberOfLines={15} fontStyle="normal">

```pseudocode
sumOfDigits(num) {
    /* Variable to store the sum of digits */
    sum = 0

    /* Continue until num becomes 0 AND sum is a single digit */
    while num > 0 OR sum > 9 {

        /* If all digits of num are processed, 
           move the current sum back to num to continue summing */
        if num == 0 {
            num = sum
            sum = 0
        }

        /* Add the last digit of num to sum */
        sum = sum + (num mod 10)

        /* Remove the last digit from num */
        num = num / 10
    }

    /* Return the final single-digit sum (digital root) */
    return sum
}
```

</CodeBlock>

