### Pseudo Code


<CodeBlock language="text" showNumberOfLines={15} fontStyle="normal">

```plaintext
insertionSortSwap(arr, n) {
    /* Start from the second element as the first is considered sorted */
    for i from 1 to n-1 {

        /* Initialize j at the current element's position */
        j = i

        /* Repeatedly swap the element with its predecessor until it's in the correct spot*/
        while j >= 1 and arr[j-1] > arr[j] {

            /* Swap adjacent elements*/
            temp = arr[j-1]
            arr[j-1] = arr[j]
            arr[j] = temp

            /* Move pointer left to continue comparisons*/
            j = j - 1
        }
    }
}
```
