### Pseudo Code


<CodeBlock language="text" showNumberOfLines={15} fontStyle="normal">

```plaintext
reverse(arr, N) {
    /* Initialize two pointers:
       i starts from the beginning, j starts from the end */
    i = 0
    j = N - 1

    /* Continue swapping elements until the pointers meet */
    while (i < j) {
        /* Swap the elements at positions i and j */
        swap(arr[i], arr[j])
        /* Move i forward */
        i++
        /* Move j backward */
        j--
    }
}

```

</CodeBlock>

### Code Implementation

<MultiLanguageCodeBlock enableMoveCode={true}>

```cpp
#include <bits/stdc++.h>
using namespace std;

class solution{
public:
    void reverse(int arr[], int N) {
        int i = 0;
        int j = N - 1;
        while (i < j) {
            swap(arr[i], arr[j]);
            i++;
            j--;
        }
    }
};

