```pseudocode
countDigits(n) {
    /* Initialize a counter to keep track of digits */
    count = 0

    /* Loop until the number becomes 0 */
    while n != 0 {
        /* Remove the last digit */
        n = n / 10

        /* Increment the digit count */
        count = count + 1
    }

    /* Return total number of digits */
    return count
}
```
