### Pseudo Code


<CodeBlock language="text" showNumberOfLines={15} fontStyle="normal">
```pseudocode
isPrime(n) {
    /* Numbers less than or equal to 1 are not prime */
    if n <= 1 {
        return false
    }

    /* Count the total number of divisors */
    count = 0

    /* Iterate from 1 up to square root of n */
    for i = 1 to while i * i <= n {
        /* If i divides n, then it is a divisor */
        if n mod i == 0 {
            count = count + 1

            /* If i and n/i are different, count both divisors */
            if i != n / i {
                count = count + 1
            }
        }
    }

    /* A prime number has exactly two divisors: 1 and itself */
    return count == 2
}
```
</CodeBlock>

### Code Implementation

<MultiLanguageCodeBlock enableMoveCode={true}>

