### Pseudo Code


<CodeBlock language="text" showNumberOfLines={15} fontStyle="normal">

```
checkPerfectNumber(num) {
    sum = 1  /* This excludes adding the number itself to the sum */
    for i from 2 to sqrt(num) {
        if (num % i == 0) {
            if (num / i == i) sum += i  /* If the number is square root of num, add only once */
            else sum += (i + num / i)   /* If i is a divisor of num, num/i is also a divisor */
        }
    }

    if(sum == num && num!=1) {        /* return true if sum of divisors is equal to num */
        return true
    } 
    return false
}
```

</CodeBlock>


