missingNumber(arr) {
    /* Find the missing number using XOR property */
    n = arr.size()
    /* Initialize num with n (last value in range) */
    num = n
    /* XOR all indices and array elements */
    for i = 0 to n - 1 {
        /* XOR cancels out matching values */
        num = num XOR i XOR arr[i]
    }

    /* Remaining value is the missing number */
    return num
}

```

