### Pseudo Code


<CodeBlock language="text" showNumberOfLines={15} fontStyle="normal">

```
missingNumber(arr) {
    /* Find the missing number using sum formula */
    n = arr.size()
    /* Calculate expected sum of numbers from 0 to n */
    expectedSum = n * (n + 1) / 2
    /* Store the actual sum of array elements */
    actualSum = 0

    /* Traverse the array and compute the sum */
    for i = 0 to n - 1 {
        actualSum = actualSum + arr[i]
    }

    /* Missing number is the difference */
    num = expectedSum - actualSum
    /* Return the missing number */
    return num
}
```

</CodeBlock>

