### Pseudo Code


<CodeBlock language="text" showNumberOfLines={15} fontStyle="normal">

```
singleNumber(arr) {
    n = arr.size()                      /* get the size of the array */
    result = 0                          /* initialize result to 0 */
    for i from 0 to n - 1 {
        result = result ^ arr[i]        /* update result by XOR with current element */
    }
    return result                       /* return the final result */
}
```

</CodeBlock>

